description:
Here is a detailed description of the floor plan for your dream house in Coimbatore:

**Floor Plan: Modern 2-Acre Residence**

**Scale: 1:100**

**Orientation: North-facing**

**Dimensions:**

* Overall building dimensions: 60 meters (196.85 feet) x 40 meters (131.23 feet)
* Total floor area: approximately 2400 square meters (25,800 square feet)

**Room Layout:**

1. **Living Room** (6.5 meters x 9 meters / 21.33 feet x 29.53 feet)
	* Located at the north-east corner of the house
	* Large windows (2.5 meters x 3 meters / 8.2 feet x 9.84 feet) on the north and east facades
	* Sliding glass door (1.5 meters x 2.5 meters / 4.92 feet x 8.2 feet) leading to the patio
	* Open-plan design with the dining area
2. **Dining Area** (4 meters x 6 meters / 13.12 feet x 19.69 feet)
	* Adjacent to the living room
	* Large window (2 meters x 3 meters / 6.56 feet x 9.84 feet) on the north facade
3. **Kitchen** (4 meters x 5 meters / 13.12 feet x 16.4 feet)
	* Located adjacent to the dining area
	* Island counter (2 meters x 1.5 meters / 6.56 feet x 4.92 feet) with sink and cooking range
	* Large window (1.5 meters x 2 meters / 4.92 feet x 6.56 feet) on the north facade
4. **Bedroom 1** (5 meters x 5 meters / 16.4 feet x 16.4 feet)
	* Located on the north-west corner of the house
	* Attached bathroom (2.5 meters x 2 meters / 8.2 feet x 6.56 feet) with shower cubicle and toilet
	* Large window (1.5 meters x 2 meters / 4.92 feet x 6.56 feet) on the north facade
5. **Bedroom 2** (5 meters x 5 meters / 16.4 feet x 16.4 feet)
	* Located on the south-west corner of the house
	* Attached bathroom (2.5 meters x 2 meters / 8.2 feet x 6.56 feet) with shower cubicle and toilet
	* Large window (1.5 meters x 2 meters / 4.92 feet x 6.56 feet) on the south facade
6. **Bedroom 3** (4.5 meters x 5 meters / 14.76 feet x 16.4 feet)
	* Located on the south-east corner of the house
	* Attached bathroom (2 meters x 1.5 meters / 6.56 feet x 4.92 feet) with shower cubicle and toilet
	* Large window (1.2 meters x 1.5 meters / 3.94 feet x 4.92 feet) on the south facade
7. **Bedroom 4** (Optional) (4 meters x 4 meters / 13.12 feet x 13.12 feet)
	* Located on the north-east corner of the house, adjacent to Bedroom 1
	* Attached bathroom (2 meters x 1.5 meters / 6.56 feet x 4.92 feet) with shower cubicle and toilet
	* Large window (1.2 meters x 1.5 meters / 3.94 feet x 4.92 feet) on the north facade
8. **Utility Room** (2 meters x 2 meters / 6.56 feet x 6.56 feet)
	* Located adjacent to the kitchen
	* Window (1 meter x 1 meter / 3.28 feet x 3.28 feet) on the north facade
9. **Wardrobe** (1.5 meters x 2 meters / 4.92 feet x 6.56 feet)
	* Located adjacent to each bedroom

**Outdoor Area:**

* **Patio** (6 meters x 8 meters / 19.69 feet x 26.25 feet)
	* Located adjacent to the living room and dining area
	* Sliding glass door (1.5 meters x 2.5 meters / 4.92 feet x 8.2 feet) leading from the living room
* **Garden** (10 meters x 15 meters / 32.81 feet x 49.21 feet)
	* Located on the south and west sides of the house
	*
